==背景==
===早年生活===
錢小豪生於香港[[中環|中環]]前稱中國街的萬宜里{{noteTag|name=守下留情|關於錢小豪出生與成長地、家庭背景、童年生活、小學母校以及接觸武術及打擂台的資料取自香港電台第二台廣播節目《守下留情》於2017年2月27日播出的訪問錄音「錢小豪訪問第一集」。}}，籍貫[[廣東省_(中華民國)|廣東]][[三水縣_(廣東)|三水]]（三水錢氏輩同鄉鄉里尚有[[錢國偉|錢國偉]]<ref>{{cite news | title=【錢國偉病逝】同錢嘉樂有血緣關係？「佢叫我廿幾年阿叔！」 | url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/541143/%E9%8C%A2%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%89%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E5%90%8C%E9%8C%A2%E5%98%89%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%89%E8%A1%80%E7%B7%A3%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82-%E4%BD%A2%E5%8F%AB%E6%88%91%E5%BB%BF%E5%B9%BE%E5%B9%B4%E9%98%BF%E5%8F%94 | page= | publisher=香港01 | date=2020-10-27 | accessdate=2021-10-04 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211004015726/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/541143/%E9%8C%A2%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%89%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E5%90%8C%E9%8C%A2%E5%98%89%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%89%E8%A1%80%E7%B7%A3%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82-%E4%BD%A2%E5%8F%AB%E6%88%91%E5%BB%BF%E5%B9%BE%E5%B9%B4%E9%98%BF%E5%8F%94 | dead-url=no }}</ref>），家有三姊一兄一弟{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}，自己排行第五{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}，其中胞兄錢嘉麟是電影幕後人員，胞弟為藝人錢嘉樂。他於兩歲搬到[[擺花街|擺花街]]一帶的住宅居住{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}，父親在該處附近開設古董裝箱搬運店舖<ref name="豪語錄 小豪語錄 錢小豪">{{cite web |url=https://tvb4life.pixnet.net/blog/post/181033173-%E8%B1%AA%E8%AA%9E%E9%8C%84-%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%E8%AA%9E%E9%8C%84-%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA-%E5%A3%B9%E5%91%A8%E5%88%8A-1266%E6%9C%9F |title=豪語錄 小豪語錄 錢小豪 |last= |first= |date=2014-06 |website= |publisher=壹周刊1266期 |access-date=2021-10-04 |quote= |archive-date=2021-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211004091743/https://tvb4life.pixnet.net/blog/post/181033173-%e8%b1%aa%e8%aa%9e%e9%8c%84-%e5%b0%8f%e8%b1%aa%e8%aa%9e%e9%8c%84-%e9%8c%a2%e5%b0%8f%e8%b1%aa-%e5%a3%b9%e5%91%a8%e5%88%8a-1266%e6%9c%9f |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}，後來舉家移居[[北角|北角]][[健康邨|健康邨]]{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。他的童年娛樂主要是到屋邨後山位置玩[[豹虎|金絲貓]]或者跑到[[賽西湖|賽西湖]]游泳{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。錢小豪曾就讀[[高主教書院|高主教書院]]（小學部）{{noteTag|資料出自香港電台第一台廣播節目《守下留情》於2019年12月10日播出的錢嘉樂訪問。}}，畢業於位於灣仔司徒拔道的私立[[嶺南小學|嶺南小學]]{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}，並在學校寄宿2年{{noteTag|name=守下留情}}。後來升讀[[嶺南中學_(香港)|嶺南中學]]，在校時不喜歡讀書兼操行差<ref>{{cite news | title=說讀書太不自由 錢小豪寧願拍戲 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFGU%2Bu0K0rHN%2B&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=73&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=4 | publisher=工商晚報 | date=1980-04-16 | accessdate=2021-10-03 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211003091854/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFGU%2Bu0K0rHN%2B&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=73&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

