殭屍”系列{{noteTag|關於錢小豪參演殭屍系列電影的資料取自香港電台第二台廣播節目《守下留情》於2017年3月2日播出的訪問錄音「錢小豪訪問第四集」。}}。1989年，錢小豪加入無綫電視<ref>{{cite news | title=錢小豪簽約無線演部頭 | url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJLdFppX7Xxih&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=78&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | page=14 | publisher=華僑日報 | date=1989-06-23 | accessdate=2021-10-03 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211003091933/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJLdFppX7Xxih&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=78&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc | dead-url=no }}</ref>，主要參演電視電影如《特技雙雄》。後期發覺港產片走下坡{{