2000年，錢小豪被發現疑似將錄影機藏在紙袋內<ref name="錢小豪獲判無罪釋放" />，偷拍在超級市場購物的女子的裙底<ref name="錢小豪獲判無罪釋放" />，超市警衛報警將他逮捕<ref name="錢小豪獲判無罪釋放" />，警方在錄影帶內發現至少30名女性的裙底鏡頭<ref name="錢小豪獲判無罪釋放" />，以「遊蕩引致他人不安」罪名提出起訴<ref>{{cite news | title=錢小豪涉 偷拍裙底春守行為兩年 | url=http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/hket/20001026/A33-04.html | page= | publisher=香港經濟日報 | date=2000-10-26 | accessdate=2021-10-02 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211002091236/http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/hket/20001026/A33-04.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。後因罪證不足獲判無罪釋放<ref name="錢小豪獲判無罪釋放" /><ref>{{cite news | title=偷拍犯遊蕩罪可判囚 | url=http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/mingpao/20010129/A07001.html | page= | publisher=明報 | date=2001-01-29 | accessdate=2021-10-02 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211002091246/http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/mingpao/20010129/A07001.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。但要付保證金二千元及[[簽保守行為|守行為]]兩年<ref name="錢小豪獲判無罪釋放" /><ref>{{cite news | title=法官斥錢小豪行為羞恥 攝裙底春光判守行為2年 | url=http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/mingpao/20001026/C01013.html | page= | publisher=明報 | date=2000-10-26 | accessdate=2021-10-02 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211002091304/http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/mingpao/20001026/C01013.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/star/hk_tw/2000-10-26/20553.html |title=偷拍女子裙底案审罢港星钱小豪被判无罪释放 |publisher=新浪娱乐 |date=2000-10-26 |accessdate=2021-10-02 |archive-date=2020-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227061041/http://ent.sina.com.cn/star/hk_tw/2000-10-26/20553.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他事後曾對外表示是酗酒誤事<ref>{{cite news | title=女友、張之亮、律師陪同會記者 錢小豪悔言酗酒誤事 | url=http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/mingpao/20000714/C02005.html | page= | publisher=明報 | date=2000-07-14 | accessdate=2021-10-02 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211002091524/http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/mingpao/20000714/C02005.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。同期與[[方中信|方中信]]、[[鄭浩南|鄭浩南]]等友人於[[尖沙咀|尖沙咀]][[山林道|山林道]]開設「Deep Blue」酒吧<ref name="錢小豪帶淚稱飲酒累事" /><ref>{{cite news | title=錢嘉樂 斥資七位數開酒吧 | url=http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/apple/20001030/C10-02.html | page= | publisher=香港蘋果日報 | date=2000-10-30 | accessdate=2021-10-02 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211002091158/http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/apple/20001030/C10-02.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2002年后，他曾淡出幕前，轉而從事導演工作。同時，錢小豪出演數部電視劇集，以[[古裝|古裝]][[武俠劇|武俠劇]]居多。及後基於不想錯過幼子成長的時光{{noteTag|name=守下留情3}}，他不再當導演{{noteTag|name=守下留情3}}，轉而專注幕前至今{{noteTag|name=守下留情3}}。2016年在《2016金花獎國際電影節》以微電影《安居》獲得「最佳男演員」<ref>{{cite news | title=《金花獎國際電影節2016》 錢小豪獲得最佳男演員 | url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/12454/%E9%87%91%E8%8A%B1%E7%8D%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%AF%802016-%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%E7%8D%B2%E5%BE%97%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E7%94%B7%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1 | page= | publisher=香港01 | date=2016-03-17 | accessdate=2021-10-03 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211003093834/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/12454/%E9%87%91%E8%8A%B1%E7%8D%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%AF%802016-%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%E7%8D%B2%E5%BE%97%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E7%94%B7%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。還成立自己的製作公司，製作中國內地網絡電影<ref>{{cite news | title=﻿錢小豪尋回流逝的「殭屍」情懷 | url=http://www.takungpao.com.hk/taiwan/text/2017/0823/107294.html | page= | publisher=大公報 | date=2017-08-23 | accessdate=2021-10-04 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211004091757/http://www.takungpao.com.hk/taiwan/text/2017/0823/107294.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一方面開設兩間拳館培育泰拳拳手<ref name="豪語錄 小豪語錄 錢小豪" /><ref>{{cite news | title=培訓泰拳精英 錢小豪想細仔做機師 | url=http://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=news4&id=73633 | page= | publisher=成報 | date=2018-06-18 | accessdate=2021-10-04 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211004091757/http://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=news4&id=73633 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=錢小豪望港代表衝金成功 陶枳樽難忘練拳辛苦到嘔 | url=https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%E6%9C%9B%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E8%A1%9D%E9%87%91%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F-%E9%99%B6%E6%9E%B3%E6%A8%BD%E9%9B%A3%E5%BF%98%E7%B7%B4%E6%8B%B3%E8%BE%9B%E8%8B%A6%E5%88%B0%E5%98%94-102800089.html | page= | publisher=星島日報 | date=2017-08-13 | accessdate=2021-10-04 | quote= | archive-date=2021-10-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211004091754/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%8F%E8%B1%AA%E6%9C%9B%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E8%A1%9D%E9%87%91%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F-%E9%99%B6%E6%9E%B3%E6%A8%BD%E9%9B%A3%E5%BF%98%E7%B7%B4%E6%8B%B3%E8%BE%9B%E8%8B%A6%E5%88%B0%E5%98%94-102800089.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

